# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:3
translate french work1_a661a5bb:

    # "Work goes fairly normally for the first three hours, then when it's nearly time to go, Mrs. Mills comes up to me."
    "Le travail se passe assez normalement pendant les trois premières heures, puis, alors que l'heure de partir approche, Mme Mills vient me voir."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:6
translate french work1_05636015:

    # "She stands close and puts a hand on my shoulder."
    "Elle se tient près de moi et pose une main sur mon épaule."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:7
translate french work1_c5e6ce57:

    # bs "You've done good work. I'm glad I decided to hire you, even though you seemed a little dense at first."
    bs "Tu as fait du bon travail. Je suis contente d'avoir décidé de t'embaucher, même si tu semblais un peu lent au début."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:8
translate french work1_d4d85540:

    # bs "I hope you'll stick around, because this week has been good."
    bs "J'espère que tu resteras, car cette semaine s'est bien passée."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:10
translate french work1_208ce8ca:

    # bs "Here's your paycheck for the week."
    bs "Voici ton chèque de paie pour la semaine."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:11
translate french work1_f9dc9fe0:

    # "She hands me a paycheck for $300."
    "Elle me tend un chèque de 300 $."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:13
translate french work1_63dc4511:

    # bs "After this check, the rest will be deposited directly to your bank account."
    bs "Après ce chèque, le reste sera versé directement sur ton compte bancaire."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:14
translate french work1_95914f27:

    # bs "Have a good weekend and I'll see you on Monday."
    bs "Passe un bon week-end et à lundi."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:15
translate french work1_bd884b3c:

    # pc "Yes, ma'am, thank you."
    pc "Oui, madame, merci."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:16
translate french work1_6e413467:

    # "I take the paycheck and leave. This money will definitely come in handy. There's plenty of things that I need, and Lisa could always use some help around the house."
    "Je prends le chèque et je pars. Cet argent va vraiment me dépanner. J’ai besoin de plein de choses, et Lisa a toujours besoin d’un coup de main à la maison."

# game/Scenes/Work/work1.rpy:19
translate french work1_cf3bc495:

    # "I tell Dana goodnight as I pass and head outside."
    "Je souhaite bonne nuit à Dana en passant et je sors."

